      "turn": 5,
      "role": "assistant",
      "agent": "tapestry",
      "content": "Both reviewers approved. Reporting final results.",
      "mockResponse": "Post-execution review complete:\n\n- **Weft** (code quality): APPROVED — well-structured changes, adequate test coverage\n- **Warp** (security): APPROVED — auth changes follow best practices, no vulnerabilities\n\nAll tasks executed and reviewed successfully. Plan execution is complete."
